high_descs: Go straight to the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn right, go toward the fridge, turn left and go across the room to the counter.
Cut the lettuce on the counter.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Put the knife in the fridge.
Turn left and go across the room to the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn around and go back to the fridge.
Chill the slice of lettuce in the fridge an pick it back up.
Turn right and go to the sink on the right.
Put the slice of lettuce on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of lettuce on the counter.

high_descs: Move forward to the island counter in front of you.
Pick up the knife that is to the left of the lettuce on the counter.
With the knife in your hand turn and go to the counter to the right of the stove.
Slice half the lettuce on the counter starting from the back.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the fridge.
Open fridge.  Place the knife on the top shelf front and center.  Close fridge.
Turn and go to the counter to the right of the stove.
Grab the middle slice of lettuce that is on the counter.
With the slice of lettuce in your hand turn and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge.  Place the lettuce to the right of the knife on the top shelf. Close fridge. Open the fridge and grab the lettuce on the top shelf.
With the lettuce in your hand go to the left side of the sink.
Place the lettuce standing up on the front part of the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Slice lettuce, put in fridge and put on counter.

high_descs: Go straight to the kitchen island
Grab the knife off of the counter
Turn right and go to the counter to the right of the oven
Slice the lettuce on the counter
Turn around and go to the fridge
Put the knife in the fridge
Turn left and go to the counter to the right of the oven
Grab a slice of the lettuce
Turn around and go to the fridge
Cool the lettuce in the fridge and then take it out
Turn left and go to the left of the sink
Put the lettuce down left of the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting cold sliced lettuce on the counter left of the sink
